The whole thing is super speechless, right?
整個事情都超級無語，對吧？

13
00:00:29.040 --> 00:00:31.040
Don't worry, you're not alone.
別擔心，你不是一個人。

14
00:00:31.040 --> 00:00:32.680
The difference in communication
溝通的差異

15
00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:35.600
