和 AI 的執行能力之間。

21
00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:45.560
And the technology to build this bridge
而建立這座橋梁的技術

22
00:00:45.560 --> 00:00:48.360
is the core ability we're going to talk about today.
是我們今天要談的核心能力。

23
00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:51.640
That's right, we call this core ability description.
沒錯，我們稱這個核心能力為描述。

24
00:00:51.640 --> 00:00:53.240
But wait a minute,
但等等，

25
