會完全不同。

38
00:01:24.800 --> 00:01:26.640
Okay, what are these three pillars?
好的，這三個支柱是什麼？

39
00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:27.840
They are
它們是

40
00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:30.920
First, the product description of the product produced by force.
首先，由強制力生產的產品的產品描述。

41
00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:33.880
Second, the process description of the guidance method.
第二，引導方法的過程描述。

42
00:01:33.880 --> 00:01:34.840
And third,
第三，

43
00:01:34.840 --> 00:01:35.840
this is very interesting,
這非常有趣，

44
00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:38.440
the performance description of the setting atmosphere.
設定氛圍的效能描述。

45
00:01:38.440 --> 00:01:40.880
As long as you cover these three pillars tightly,
只要你緊緊掌握這三個支柱，

46
00:01:40.880 --> 00:01:44.440
