你與 AI 的溝通就會很穩定。

47
00:01:44.440 --> 00:01:47.640
Okay, let's start with the first one.
好的，讓我們從第一個開始。

48
00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:51.640
How exactly do you want to accurately describe what you want?
你究竟要如何準確地描述你想要的東西？

49
00:01:51.640 --> 00:01:54.400
This is the so-called product description.
這就是所謂的產品描述。

50
00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:55.320
To put it simply,
簡單來說，

51
00:01:55.320 --> 00:01:56.840
the ability of product description
產品描述的能力

52
00:01:56.840 --> 00:02:00.120
is that you have to be able to clearly define
就是你必須能夠清楚地定義

53
00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:03.720
what kind of product you want AI to create in the end.
你最終想讓 AI 創造什麼樣的產品。

54
00:02:03.720 --> 00:02:05.040
Not just roughly,
不只是粗略地，

55
00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:06.600
but very accurately.
而是非常準確。

56
00:02:06.600 --> 00:02:08.760
How big is the difference?
差異有多大呢？

57
00:02:08.760 --> 00:02:10.480
Come on, let's imagine
來吧，讓我們想像一下

58
00:02:10.480 --> 00:02:11.560
you tell AI,
你告訴 AI，

59
00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:13.720
hey, help me prepare dinner.
嘿，幫我準備晚餐。

60
00:02:13.720 --> 00:02:15.880
This is too vague.
這太模糊了。

61
00:02:15.880 --> 00:02:17.640
How does he know what you want to eat?
他怎麼知道你想吃什麼？

62
00:02:17.640 --> 00:02:19.480
But if you change the way you say,
但如果你改變說法，

63
00:02:19.480 --> 00:02:21.800
hey, I want to make Italian chicken noodles.
嘿，我想做義大利雞肉麵。

64
00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:23.080
Give me a recipe.
給我一份食譜。

65
00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:24.720
You have to have all the ingredients
你必須有所有的食材

66
00:02:24.720 --> 00:02:27.240
