和超詳細的烹飪步驟在上面。

67
00:02:27.240 --> 00:02:29.480
Look, is this super clear?
看，這是不是超清楚？

68
00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:32.160
This is a 100% product description.
這就是 100% 的產品描述。

69
00:02:32.160 --> 00:02:33.400
So the point is,
所以重點是，

70
00:02:33.400 --> 00:02:37.440
please don't let AI guess what you want.
請不要讓 AI 猜測你想要什麼。

71
00:02:37.440 --> 00:02:39.200
You have to tell him clearly,
你必須清楚地告訴他，

72
00:02:39.200 --> 00:02:41.320
hey, what is the background of this job?
嘿，這份工作的背景是什麼？

73
00:02:41.320 --> 00:02:42.760
What do you want him to do?
你想讓他做什麼？

74
00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:44.440
Make it clear step by step.
逐步說清楚。

75
00:02:44.440 --> 00:02:46.360
What kind of format do you want to use in the end?
你最終想要什麼格式？

76
00:02:46.360 --> 00:02:47.920
Wordang or簡報?
Word 文檔還是簡報？

77
00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:49.720
Then who wants to see this thing?
那麼誰想看這個東西？

78
00:02:49.720 --> 00:02:52.200
Is it for the boss or the client?
是給老闆還是客戶？

79
00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:53.640
What kind of style do you want in the end?
你最終想要什麼樣的風格？

80
00:02:53.640 --> 00:02:55.640
More shocking or more lively?
更震撼還是更生動？

81
00:02:55.640 --> 00:02:57.360
These things have to be said clearly.
這些事情必須說清楚。

82
00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:59.800
Okay, it's not enough to know what you want.
好的，僅僅知道你想要什麼是不夠的。

83
00:02:59.800 --> 00:03:01.840
Sometimes more importantly,
有時候更重要的是，

84
00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:04.560
how do you guide AI to do?
你如何指導 AI 去做？

85
00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:06.720
This brings us to the second pillar,
這引出了第二個支柱，

86
00:03:06.720 --> 00:03:08.240
the process description.
流程描述。

87
00:03:08.240 --> 00:03:09.680
The process description,
流程描述，

88
00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:10.640
in private,
私下裡，

89
00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:11.760
is to guide AI
是指導 AI

90
00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:14.320
on how to do this thing.
如何做這件事。

91
00:03:14.320 --> 00:03:15.760
Remember, sometimes
記住，有時候

92
00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:17.160
give AI a map,
給 AI 一張地圖，

93
00:03:17.160 --> 00:03:18.520
that is, that process,
也就是說那個流程，

94
00:03:18.520 --> 00:03:20.160
will be more important
會比更重要

95
00:03:20.160 --> 00:03:21.360
than you just tell him the end,
你只是告訴他最終結果，

96
00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:22.400
more important,
更重要，

97
00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:23.800
and more efficient.
也更高效。

98
00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:25.640
How to guide?
怎樣指導？

99
00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:27.480
There are probably several ways.
大概有幾種方式。

100
00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:29.440
You can give him a manual,
你可以給他一份手冊，

101
00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:31.720
which is a guide to some major directions.
即某些主要方向的指南。

102
00:03:31.720 --> 00:03:34.080
Or you can give him a recipe,
或者你可以給他一個食譜，

103
00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:36.200
telling him in detail
詳細地告訴他

104
00:03:36.200 --> 00:03:37.320
what to do first,
先做什麼，

105
00:03:37.320 --> 00:03:38.560
what to do second.
再做什麼。

106
00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:42.040
You can even show it to him in person
你甚至可以親身示範給他

107
00:03:42.040 --> 00:03:43.120
and use some examples
並用一些例子

108
00:03:43.120 --> 00:03:45.280
to let him learn your method.
讓他學習你的方法。

109
00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:46.280
Think about it.
想一想。

110
00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:48.160
Although AI's knowledge library is wide,
雖然 AI 的知識庫很廣泛，

111
00:03:48.160 --> 00:03:51.080
but he doesn't know the unique situation you have.
但他不知道你所處的獨特情況。

112
00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.640
So you can tell him
所以你可以告訴他

113
00:03:52.640 --> 00:03:54.720
I have some specific information here,
我這裡有一些特定的信息，

114
00:03:54.720 --> 00:03:56.520
