而具有不同的行為模式。

139
00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:39.600
Really, it's very similar to people.
真的，這非常像人類。

140
00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:43.200
This is the most important part of performance description.
這是性能描述最重要的部分。

141
00:04:43.200 --> 00:04:46.040
You have to define the behavior mode
你必須定義行為模式

142
00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:48.640
