我現在需要什麼樣的思考夥伴？

151
00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:06.960
Do I need a partner who will challenge me and refute me?
我需要一個會挑戰我、反駁我的夥伴嗎？

152
00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:10.080
Or do I need someone who is obedient and follows me?
還是我需要一個順從並跟隨我的人？

153
00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:13.120
I want him to give me super detailed information
我想要它給我超詳細的信息

154
00:05:13.120 --> 00:05:13.720
or
還是

155
00:05:13.720 --> 00:05:15.520
just focus on the point.
只關注重點。

156
00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:18.360
I need him to explain the thinking process of each step
我需要它解釋每一步的思考過程

157
00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:20.440
or just give me the answer directly.
還是直接給我答案。

158
00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:21.240
You see,
你看，

159
00:05:21.240 --> 00:05:22.800
these choices will create
這些選擇會創造

160
00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:24.800
