完全不同的 AI 夥伴。

161
00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:27.250
Okay, we've finished reading the three pillars.
好的，我們已經讀完了三個支柱。

162
00:05:28.650 --> 00:05:31.770
When you combine the three descriptions
當你結合這三個描述時

163
00:05:31.770 --> 00:05:34.130
of the product, process, and performance
關於你剛才提到的產品、流程和績效

164
00:05:34.130 --> 00:05:35.930
that you just mentioned,
你剛才提到的

165
00:05:35.930 --> 00:05:38.370
what magical things will happen?
會發生什麼神奇的事情？

166
00:05:38.370 --> 00:05:39.810
The final result is
最終的結果是

167
00:05:39.810 --> 00:05:41.210
you turn AI from
你把 AI 從

168
00:05:41.210 --> 00:05:42.810
an assistant you know
一個你認識的助手

169
00:05:42.810 --> 00:05:44.450
who is very common, like a can,
一個非常普遍的，就像罐頭一樣

170
00:05:44.450 --> 00:05:46.130
into a person who is completely
轉變成一個完全的人

171
00:05:46.170 --> 00:05:47.330
a person who knows you
一個認識你的人

172
00:05:47.330 --> 00:05:50.170
and can help you solve those super complicated problems.
能幫你解決那些超級複雜的問題。

173
00:05:50.170 --> 00:05:52.010
A super powerful tool.
一個超級強大的工具。

174
00:05:52.010 --> 00:05:54.770
So this brings a question that is worth thinking about.
所以這提出了一個值得思考的問題。

175
00:05:54.770 --> 00:05:56.210
After listening to these today,
聽了今天的這些內容之後

176
00:05:56.210 --> 00:05:58.170
what kind of thinking partner
你想首先創造什麼樣的思考夥伴

177
00:05:58.170 --> 00:06:00.170
do you want to create first?
？
